### Login and obtain JWT
POST {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@studiobooking.test",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Get packages (requires token)
GET {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/packages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get timetable
GET {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/timetable?businessId=1&date=2026-06-14
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Book class
POST {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduleId": 3,
  "packageId": 1
}

### Join waitlist
POST {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/waitlist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduleId": 2,
  "packageId": 9
}

### Cancel booking
POST {{StudioBooking.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": 1
}
